#: ../../user/advanced-topics/gui-domain.rst:48
#: 484f653ae76743e99cf18c15b5bf0b06
msgid "GPU GUI domain (``sys-gui-gpu``)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/advanced-topics/gui-domain.rst:51
#: b51db10d0deb407e8e219ad0f481096b
msgid ""
"Here, we describe how to setup ``sys-gui-gpu`` which is a GUI domain with"
" *GPU passthrough* in `GUI domain <https://www.qubes-"
"os.org/news/2020/03/18/gui-domain/>`__."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/advanced-topics/gui-domain.rst:53
#: cd6845d2434e499293c5eb6ea83d9e3c
msgid ""
"**Note:** the purpose of ``sys-gui-gpu`` is to improve Qubes OS security "
"by detaching the GPU from dom0, this is not intended to improve GPU "
"related performance within qubes, and this will not improve performance."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/advanced-topics/gui-domain.rst:55
